OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bryan
OL,4,CSamain
OL,6,FBryan Samain, Age: 99, Royal Marine
OL,7,FCommandos
OL,9,FInterviewed 19 February 2024
OL,11,FArriving a week after D-Day, and among
OL,12,Fthe first reinforcements, Mr Samain
OL,13,Fwas an officer with 45 Royal Marine
OL,14,FCommando.
OL,16,FHe was sent to the front line less
OL,17,Fthan two hours after crossing the
OL,18,FChannel by sea.
OL,20,F"It was a relatively quiet part of the
OL,21,Ffront," he said.
