OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bryan
OL,4,CSamain
OL,6,F"Quite a lot of marshy country so
OL,7,Fthere weren't tanks around.
OL,9,F"But there was a division of German
OL,10,Ftroops who consisted of veterans who
OL,11,Fhad fought on the Russian front, and
OL,12,Fthere were occasional clashes with
OL,13,Fthem because they retreated back from
OL,14,Fus and dug themselves into different
OL,15,Femplacements."
OL,17,FA section commander, Mr Samain became
OL,18,Fthe unit's sniper officer.
