OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bryan
OL,4,CSamain
OL,6,F"There were four Marine-rank snipers
OL,7,Fand one had already accounted for 32
OL,8,Fof the enemy in the first week of
OL,9,Ffighting," Mr Samain said.
OL,11,F"We went out on a regular patrol
OL,12,Ffacing woodland and hid up.
OL,14,F"A sniper has to prepare a hide in
OL,15,Fwhich he can conceal himself and lie
OL,16,Fmotionless for a long time, an hour or
OL,17,Fso.
