OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bryan
OL,4,CSamain
OL,6,F"Nine times out of ten you will see
OL,7,Fsomething and have a shot at it - then
OL,8,Fyou have to lie perfectly still
OL,9,Fbecause they are going to wonder where
OL,10,Fthe hell it's come from.
OL,12,F"The worst thing you can do is start
OL,13,Fthinking about dashing away."
OL,15,FLater Mr Samain became the unit's
OL,16,Fintelligence officer because the
OL,17,Fprevious one was killed on D-Day.
