OL,4,CSamain
OL,6,FHis role included leading the
OL,7,Finterrogation of prisoners, assisted
OL,8,Fby German Jews who had joined the
OL,9,FBritish Army.
OL,11,FThis helped build up a picture of
OL,12,Fenemy positions and movements. And he
OL,13,Fupdated officers around him, acting as
OL,14,F''a mobile newspaper'' in his words.
OL,16,FAfter the war he became a journalist.
